Package: NeStage
Type: Package
Title: Effective Population Size from Stage-Structured Populations
Version: 0.8.0
Date: 2026-03-07
Authors@R: person("Raymond L.", "Tremblay",
           email = "raymond.tremblay@gmail.com",
           role  = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6896-5844"))
Description: Computes effective population size (Ne) and the Ne/N ratio for
    stage-structured populations using the matrix population model framework
    of Yonezawa (2000). Functions are provided for sexually reproducing,
    clonally reproducing, and mixed (sexual + clonal) populations. Includes
    sensitivity and elasticity analyses for Ne/N with respect to vital rates.
